Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.26,0:00:04.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.84,0:00:11.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:23.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.55,0:00:32.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.63,0:00:42.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.34,0:00:48.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.31,0:00:52.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.15,0:00:55.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:08.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.37,0:01:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.01,0:01:24.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守護著世界和平的正義秘密結社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓諸位都能見到明日的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的夥伴、愛與真實的友方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到地球戰騎隊網站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責引導各位的愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:02:03.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於想瀏覽的頁面\N請從這邊的選項選取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉\N本網頁目前還在製作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉\N本網頁目前還在製作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉...\N這算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都還在製作中嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是粗糙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是英司的惡作劇呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是地圖吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直和小鬼的塗鴉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像英司會做的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「華麗的再會」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂~真的是這個方向嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是照這地圖走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向應該沒錯才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們都走了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧我們該不會迷路了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就只有一條路耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之也只有繼續走了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.25,0:03:09.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的在23區共計四人\N目前正以C程序應對中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把畫面轉到螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是一般百姓\N即刻開始查對身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.46,0:03:19.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用調查了\N我認得這群孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至此集團會議可以結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦妳們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生\N保安部有狀況向您報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的有訪客光臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訪客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家再也走不動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早就穿過森林了才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都看不到像出口的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.59,0:03:53.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是徹底迷路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個騎著馬的男人\N和一個騎著馬的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那位女僕姊姊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認得她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是英司住的城堡裡的女僕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:14.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是上次在地下室\N救了小弓的大姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸位是英司的朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是葛萊因.桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎蒞臨聖日耳曼城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次沒能向妳道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在看起來很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到城門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好華麗的城堡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的城堡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形狀也很稀奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他就在這裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐不下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有夠沒出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家也...快要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外星異種\N又再度開始行動了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡的"鬼"也就跟著復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訪客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有這樣的預定才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N似乎是來拜訪英司少爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位是英司少爺的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的我們是高中同班同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同班同學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看來挺好的嘛英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.62,0:06:30.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小香大鳥高須...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們會在這兒啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那丫頭...\N為什麼和斗牙這麼親熱呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.63,0:06:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是英司少爺的朋友而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露妹妹好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多看起來也不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在做什麼英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算把這座城\N變成觀光景點是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家就是一肚子鳥氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛超重神賭命戰鬥的\N明明就是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻被當成EFA的功勞了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是自外星異種手下\N保護這星球上的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人到底怎麼想並不是重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們戰敗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這星球的生命也將滅絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來這裡是不是會讓英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他本來就常常被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在擔心英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是妳想的那樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜引導貴賓們參觀城內吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.80,0:07:57.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始\N為各位介紹聖日耳曼城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位有什麼特別想看的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.68,0:08:02.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司也有駕駛對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家想要去看看女僕們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我也想看女僕\N超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就從\N超重機組機庫開始介紹起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.53,0:08:21.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會在合神後\N會變成超重神的雙腳組件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的那是G攻擊機與G打擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他開的就是這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.21,0:08:35.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的是由英司少爺\N駕駛這架G攻擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐駕駛另一架G打擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來與外星異種進行作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他還真的是在保衛地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有下面的電鑽戰車呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好...好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那輛叫作G鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是琉菜小姐與我駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也有駕駛呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N不過我還不太能進入狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~妳好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害對吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊可是我們女僕的代表呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒真是太棒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種不採用螺旋造型的鑽頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人能感受到那份堅持之美啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:16.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你的嗜好挺不錯的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的貴賓是英司少爺的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家可要打起精神來烹調啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛拳! 飛拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帥斃了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然超級機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不把拳頭打出去\N感覺就不夠熱血了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是光線技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光線! 光線!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅只要一熱衷起來\N就完全不顧周遭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點高須也半斤八兩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.07,0:10:06.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我將為各位介紹司令室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令室是作什麼的地方啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以稱作這個城的頭腦的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜前去野餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐...是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:31.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要開始歡迎貴賓的野餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很快樂的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.14,0:10:44.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向野餐出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的都來野餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還得開著超重機組來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外星異種恢復活動的此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時時做好準備\N是我們地球戰騎隊的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一板一眼喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸君手邊都有飲料了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就不用拘泥小節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這個女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對就是英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他頭一次來城裡的打扮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦~還挺適合他的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋! 我那是逼不得已的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.58,0:12:06.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎唷那你偷窺女僕們更衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是逼不得已的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我洗澡的時候也被英司偷窺過!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你好下流喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好下流哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你好下流是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你是個年青小伙子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像那一晚也是...對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一晚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我們什麼都沒有做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.68,0:12:36.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦\N哪有人會把英司當回事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下\N剛剛那句話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉、瑪莉妮雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起喝啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷~文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛和兩個小妹妹\N靜靜窩在一邊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧~你也給我喝啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說\N你沒辦法把成熟女人當對象呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:02.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喝醉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.11,0:13:05.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?你身上挺香的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這味道怎麼這麼讓我懷念呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別客氣盡情的喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得你過的真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你見到綾香姊了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見到老姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是一樣的消失中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼消失了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有在找她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼找...怎麼找...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣哪裡都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.54,0:14:03.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~羅羅多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的野生者呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.24,0:14:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放你身上蘊藏的野生之力\N實現我等的心願...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把綾香找出來吧!\N白色之獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都很盡興的樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉辦這次的野餐真是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很盡興的樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊大家都很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沖繩一定很好玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很好玩才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的很好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三位\N看起來並不是很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的! 我們好的很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然麻煩客人做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零嘴也要全部拿來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小香發生什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像壓到什麼了耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說壓到什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擠死人了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個\N幹嘛全塞到我這裡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起因為情況緊急就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就忍著點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不快找到她們的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露那邊情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.12,0:16:05.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...我這裡也沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現G鑽機機體尚無損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認駕駛艙內有兩個生命反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人皆平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙快點停住它啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用\N對方不接受超重皇下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將繼續追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去和你會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家跟我來唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺請您快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快跟上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很中意那裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都停不下來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅為什麼停不住它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是個人鎖定在運作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一切指命都不被接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想停住它\N只能先用萬用鑰匙重開機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再進行合神才行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬用鑰匙呢?\N妳想我會帶它來野餐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要重開機就行了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的話\N必須直接與G鑽機接觸才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我進去裡面進行重開機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各超重機組準備合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在G鑽機重開的同時進行合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧彈劾號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位妳們沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位你們沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是兩位有了什麼萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家...人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了她們都沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一個吧愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.36,0:20:06.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊笑一個嘛愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.84,0:20:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害妳們\N遇到這麼恐怖的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀媚月小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還在G鑽機裡堆酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...好想吐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你腦袋上的是羅羅多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠為什麼會在那裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很中意那裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:21:00.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個服裝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也罷挺像那男人會有的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張肖像畫\N是在18世紀時所繪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18世紀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.74,0:21:18.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N肖像上的人是聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.64,0:21:21.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是法國貴族也是鍊金術士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.44,0:21:25.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在當時又被稱為時間的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術士和時間的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖日耳曼伯爵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去做更深入的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.63,0:21:39.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.07,0:21:54.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想...休息喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.39,0:22:07.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.56,0:22:11.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.40,0:22:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.67,0:22:28.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.69,0:22:41.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.63,0:22:47.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.06,0:22:53.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.57,0:22:56.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:23:03.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.81,0:23:05.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.18,0:23:10.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.69,0:23:13.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:22.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.27,0:23:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為慰勞旅行\N所以要去泡溫泉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是感謝桑德曼先生\N太感謝他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是高興的時候啦\N裘依露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.84,0:23:37.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看外星異種又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外\N好像還有群身份不明的人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.65,0:23:42.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在注意著我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斗牙少爺的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.82,0:23:47.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回\N「熱鬥!愚裸美溫泉!!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.36,0:23:51.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回我們也將照料各位的和平哦


